ComicInfo.Summary: Hell's a City...: The Warheads are sent to the Un-Earth to confront Death's Head II, who is inadvertantly causing an anomaly. Upon arriving, they ally themselves with him against attacking demons. After watching a little girl die, Death's Head II and the Warheads return to Earth to confront the Mys-Tech board on why they'd introduced demons to the Un-Earth.
